<p class="small-italic"><a href="https://youtu.be/UsaoajXERfY?si=m6PayV3BuU8TnqTF">Video source</a> • <a href="https://rocketlabcorp.com/space-systems/gauss-propulsion/">Thruster info</a></p></div>
            <div class="media-video">
